Tools
=====

Source code
-----------

You can [[fetch Tails source code using Git|contribute/git]].

Bugtracker
----------

Tails tasks are managed in Redmine at [[!tails_redmine "" desc="labs.riseup.net"]].

Tails heavy tasks are often [[drafted as blueprints|blueprint]].

